default entry: src/index.js
default output: dist/main.js

css-loader: handles css files
styles-loader: injects css into style tags
MiniCssPlugin loader: creates css file (instead of style tag)

loader arrays work from back to front

sideEffects - property in package.json that will tree shake deps that are unused but bundled via side effects

if you use `optimization` field to minify css, you'll have to explicitly minify js with terser-webpack-plugin